037package org.jfree.chart.api;
038
039/**
040 * Represents several possible interpretations for an (x, y) coordinate.
041 */
042public enum XYCoordinateType {
043
044    /** The (x, y) coordinates represent a point in the data space. */
045    DATA,
046
047    /**
048     * The (x, y) coordinates represent a relative position in the data space.
049     * In this case, the values should be in the range (0.0 to 1.0).
050     */
051    RELATIVE,
052
053    /**
054     * The (x, y) coordinates represent indices in a dataset.
055     * In this case, the values should be in the range (0.0 to 1.0).
056     */
057    INDEX
058
059}
